quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  91,1,"M wẽen ne wĩntoogã la a sõorã."
  91,2,"La ne kiuugã t'a sã n wa pʋglg wĩndgã."
  91,3,"La ne wĩntoogã t'a sã n wɑ vẽnege."
  91,4,"La ne yʋng t'a sã n wa lut kiuugã."
  91,5,"La ne saagã la bũmb ning sẽn me-a wã."
  91,6,"La M wẽen ne Tẽngã la ɑ yɑdgrã."
  91,7,"La ne yõore, la bũmb ning sẽn yõgen-a wã."
  91,8,"t'A lεεms-a (yõorã) a kɩɩsgã la a wẽn-zoeerã!"
  91,9,"Hakɩɩka ned ning sẽn yɩlg-a tɩlgame."
  91,10,"La hakɩɩka! Ned ning sẽn rẽgem-a bõname."
  91,11,"Samuud rãmb yagsame b kedgrã yĩnga."
  91,12,"B sẽn wa n tʋms b zu-be-nedã."
  91,13,"Tɩ Wẽnd Tẽn-tʋʋmã yeel-ba: ""gũus-y Wẽnd yʋgemdã la a yũnugrã."
  91,14,"Tɩ b yags-a, n kõs yʋgemdã, tɩ b Soabã halk-b b zunuubã yĩnga, n zems b sɩbgrã tɩ yɑɑ yembre."
  91,15,"A mɑɑnɑ rẽ n nɑms-bɑ, n pɑ yaeesd yell bɑɑ fʋɩ nɑ n wɑ yɩ ye."
